text: Terval is a commune. It is in Pays de la Loire in the Vendée department in west France. The municipality was created on 1 January 2023 and consists of the former communes of La Tardière (the seat), Breuil-Barret and La Chapelle- aux-Lys. == References == Category:2023 establishments in France Category:Communes in Vendée
title: Terval
